</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_531" id="265r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Seiczen Marschalk czu Oberndorff
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, vicztumb in Obern
                                                Bayern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her vicztumb, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                                Burkhart Hofners, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                                                dieners, wegen, lassen wir ew wissen, daz derselb
                                                unser diener <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> niht
                                                anheim ist; und <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                                                herheim kumt, so <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                in durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen gern
                                                czu reden seczen und ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wissen lassen,
                                                ob die <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen an uns vordert.
                                                  <add>Und</add> wo wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dinste
                                                beweisen mochten, des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                                                wir willig und teten das
                                                  <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
